BSgate({theta_1_1}, {phi_1_1}) | (q[1], q[2])
BSgate({theta_1_2}, {phi_1_2}) | (q[0], q[1])
Rgate({varphi_1_0}) | (q[0])
Rgate({varphi_1_1}) | (q[1])
Rgate({varphi_1_2}) | (q[2])
Dgate({a_0}, 0) | (q[0])
Dgate({a_1}, 0) | (q[1])
Dgate({a_2}, 0) | (q[2])
